ECE 254: Operating Systems Lab 3/Lab 4
Bounded Producer/Consumer Problem Implemented in two ways with
Message Passing and Threads
Includes both .c files intended to be run on a posix compatible linux OS
and Kiel projects intended to be run on the in-lab Kiel boards
Mohit Gupta m23gupta 
Siddharth Ramesh s7ramesh

To build linux files run:
1) for the shared memeory
gcc -lrt -lm -lpthread lab3_threads.c -o produce

2) for the message queuey
gcc -lrt -lm lab3_mq.c -o produce


The Kiel projects are two directories, each containing the project space for the Message Queue and Shared Memory projects
Set target to ram or simulator and load/debug

